title: ARLE 请求调度状态机 (commit 38f28d09)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Submitted : HTTP / agent 提交
    Submitted --> Queued : 入队待 admission
    Queued --> Admitted : admission policy<br/>(scheduler/policy.rs)
    Admitted --> Prefilling : 进入 chunked prefill
    Prefilling --> Prefilling : chunk 未完成<br/>继续下一 token 块
    Prefilling --> Decoding : 首 token 产出<br/>切 decode-priority batching
    Decoding --> Decoding : per-token 解码循环

    Decoding --> SpecPath : 进入投机解码<br/>(spec_path.rs)
    SpecPath --> Decoding : accepted (commit drafted tokens)
    SpecPath --> Decoding : rejected (single-token fallback)

    Decoding --> Preempted : 压力命中 eviction policy
    Prefilling --> Preempted : 压力命中 eviction policy
    Preempted --> Queued : 重新排队等待 admission

    Decoding --> Stopped : EOS / stop seq / max_tokens
    Stopped --> Released : 释放 KV / 归还 slot
    Released --> [*]

